[normal]“
[normal]I am four years old. I make bricks. I hurt here and here.” – 
[normal]Saad
[normal],
[normal] aged four
[normal], as he points to his knees and shoulders. He works with his family to make concrete blocks. They are paid $8 for every 100 they make. 
