[normal]“Every time she comes from the center, I feel she is happier and happier,” says Laila. “She always brings some kind of drawing or craft with her, and now she wants to take her 6-year-old
[normal] sister with her, too.”
[normal] – 
[normal]Lalia, who fled Syria with her two children, aged eight and six
[normal],
[normal] after their father was killed.
